description: Wästbygg Gruppen AB engages in the provision of construction and property development services. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 315 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-10-13. The firm is engaged in building and developing homes, commercial buildings, community properties and logistics and industrial facilities. The operations are conducted through three segments: Housing, Commercial and Logistics and industry. Wastbygg Gruppen operates in Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Finland.
